#More nicely formatted README coming soon.

Trowl is a simple notification application that displays Growl messages
based on twitter updates.

Dependencies:
    python twitter module - http://code.google.com/p/python-twitter/
    Growl Python module - http://growl.info/documentation/developer/python-support.php

